  "prompt": "What are the best fps games for PC for example: Battlefield?",
  "response": "There are many great first-person shooter (FPS) games for PC, and the best ones can vary depending on individual preferences. Here are some of the most highly regarded FPS games as of the latest updates:\n\n1. **Battlefield Series**:\n   - *Battlefield 2042*: The latest installment offers large-scale battles and dynamic weather effects.\n   - *Battlefield 5*: Set during WWII, it features immersive graphics and expansive multiplayer modes.\n   - *Battlefield 1*: Focuses on WWI, known for its historical setting and intense gameplay.\n\n2. **Call of Duty Series**:\n   - *Call of Duty: Modern Warfare (2019)*: A reboot that offers a fresh take on the classic modern combat setting.\n   - *Call of Duty: Warzone*: A free-to-play battle royale game that has been very popular.\n   - *Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War*: Another modern entry with a focus on Cold War-era combat.\n\n3. **Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS:GO)**: A highly competitive and skill-based FPS that has been a staple in esports.\n\n4. **Apex Legends**: A free-to-play battle royale game that features unique characters with special abilities.\n\n5. **Rainbow Six Siege**: Focuses on tactical gameplay and destructible environments, with a strong emphasis on team coordination.\n\n6. **DOOM Series**:\n   - *DOOM Eternal*: Known for its fast-paced and brutal action with great graphics and level design.\n   - *DOOM (2016)*: A reboot of the classic series with modern graphics and gameplay mechanics.\n\n7. **Overwatch**: A team-based shooter with a diverse cast of characters, each with unique abilities.\n\n8. **Valorant**: A tactical shooter developed by Riot Games, combining precise shooting mechanics with character abilities.\n\n9. **Escape from Tarkov**: A hardcore and realistic online first-person action game with RPG elements.\n\n10. **Far Cry Series**:\n    - *Far Cry 6*: The latest entry, set in a tropical paradise with a narrative-driven campaign.\n    - *Far Cry 5*: Set in Montana, offers a rich open-world experience.\n\n11. **Metro Series**:\n    - *Metro Exodus*: A post-apocalyptic FPS with a strong narrative and atmospheric environments.\n\nThese games are known for their engaging gameplay, graphics, and community support, making them some of the best FPS games available for PC.",
